  <h3 id="other-technical">Other Technical Checks</h3>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>HTTPS enforcement</strong> - Detects non-HTTPS pages</li>
    <li><strong>Mobile viewport meta tag</strong> - Required for mobile-friendly pages</li>
    <li><strong>Charset declaration</strong> - Proper character encoding</li>
    <li><strong>DOCTYPE declaration</strong> - Valid HTML5 doctype</li>
