    <li><strong>Keyword stuffing</strong> - Single word appears >5% of content</li>
    <li><strong>Hidden text</strong> - Text using CSS to hide from users</li>
    <li><strong>Low text-to-HTML ratio</strong> - Too much code, too little content</li>
    <li><strong>Excessive bold/strong tags</strong> - Over-optimization signal</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="link-analysis">Link Analysis Checks (15+)</h2>

  <h3 id="internal-links">Internal Link Issues</h3>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>No internal links</strong> - Orphan pages with no internal links pointing to them</li>
    <li><strong>Too many links</strong> - Pages with >100 links (dilutes PageRank)</li>
    <li><strong>Nofollow on internal links</strong> - Internal links shouldn't typically be nofollowed</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 id="anchor-text">Anchor Text Quality</h3>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Empty anchor text</strong> - Links with no visible text</li>
    <li><strong>Generic anchors</strong> - "Click here", "Read more", "Learn more"</li>
    <li><strong>Excessive same-anchor links</strong> - Many links with identical text</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 id="external-links">External Link Issues</h3>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Missing rel="noopener"</strong> - Security risk for <code>target="_blank"</code> links</li>
    <li><strong>Broken external links</strong> - Links to non-existent pages</li>
    <li><strong>Excessive nofollow</strong> - Too many nofollowed links may look unnatural</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="image-optimization">Image Optimization Checks (10+)</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Missing alt text</strong> - Images without <code>alt</code> attribute</li>
    <li><strong>Empty alt attribute</strong> - <code>alt=""</code> (valid for decorative images only)</li>
    <li><strong>Alt text too long</strong> - More than 125 characters</li>
    <li><strong>Missing dimensions</strong> - No <code>width</code>/<code>height</code> attributes (causes CLS)</li>
    <li><strong>Generic filenames</strong> - image1.jpg, photo.png, etc.</li>
    <li><strong>Missing lazy loading</strong> - Below-fold images without <code>loading="lazy"</code></li>
  </ul>

