    <li><strong>Invalid hreflang codes</strong> - Incorrect language or country codes</li>
    <li><strong>Missing x-default</strong> - No default/fallback version specified</li>
    <li><strong>Self-referencing hreflang missing</strong> - Page should reference itself</li>
    <li><strong>Content-Language mismatch</strong> - Header doesn't match hreflang</li>
  </ul>

